---
// No props — static content
---

<div data-module="about-grid">

  <aside data-module="about-photo-col">
    <img
      src="/matt-pyle-headshot.jpg"
      alt="Matt Pyle"
      width="520"
      height="520"
      loading="eager"
      class="headshot"
    />
    <div class="identity-card">
      <p class="id-name">MATT PYLE</p>
      <p class="id-title">Director of Growth</p>
      <p class="id-org">Temporal Technologies</p>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <div class="about-bio">

    <section aria-labelledby="bio-background">
      <h2 id="bio-background">Background</h2>
      <div class="bio-body">
        <p>
          Eyup! <br /><br />
          I think about product-led growth, marketing strategy, and the intersection of AI with how modern
          marketing teams actually work.
        </p>
        <p>
          I build software as a hobbyist — not a professional engineer, but someone who increasingly vibe codes to bring ideas to life. Most of the projects are small and questionably useful.
          Occasionally one escapes into the wild.
        </p>
        <p>This site is where I think out loud.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="bio-interests">
      <h2 id="bio-interests">Areas of interest</h2>
      <ul data-module="topics-grid" role="list">
        <li><span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true">›</span>Product-led growth</li>
        <li><span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true">›</span>SaaS marketing strategy</li>
        <li><span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true">›</span>AI + marketing workflows</li>
        <li><span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true">›</span>Building software (the hobbyist kind)</li>
        <li><span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true">›</span>Good coffee, taken seriously</li>
        <li><span class="bullet" aria-hidden="true">›</span>Asking "why does this actually work?"</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="bio-connect">
      <h2 id="bio-connect">Connect</h2>
      <nav aria-label="Contact and social links" class="connect-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/mattpyle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <span class="connect-label">GITHUB</span>
          <span class="connect-handle">github.com/mattpyle ↗</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/matt-pyle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <span class="connect-label">LINKEDIN</span>
          <span class="connect-handle">linkedin.com/in/matt-pyle ↗</span>
        </a>
      </nav>
    </section>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  [data-module="about-grid"] {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 12px 40px 80px;
  }

  [data-module="about-photo-col"] {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .headshot {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 15%;
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .identity-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding: 14px 16px;
  }

  .id-name { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: .08em; color: var(--color-heading); margin: 0; }
  .id-title { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .05em; color: var(--color-muted); margin: 6px 0 0; }
  .id-org   { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .05em; color: var(--color-label); margin: 2px 0 0; }

  .about-bio { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 36px; padding-top: 2px; }

  section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: normal;
    letter-spacing: .16em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .bio-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }

  .bio-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .bio-body a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-accent-underline);
    transition: text-decoration-color .15s ease;
  }

  .bio-body a:hover { text-decoration-color: var(--color-accent); }

  [data-module="topics-grid"] {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px 24px;
  }

  [data-module="topics-grid"] li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .bullet { color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; }

  .connect-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }

  .connect-links a {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color .15s ease, background .15s ease;
  }

  .connect-links a:hover { border-color: var(--color-accent); background: var(--color-accent-wash); }

  .connect-label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: .12em; color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .connect-handle { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--color-muted); transition: color .15s ease; }
  .connect-links a:hover .connect-handle { color: var(--color-accent); }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    [data-module="about-grid"] { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
    [data-module="about-photo-col"] { max-width: 280px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; }
    [data-module="topics-grid"] { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    [data-module="about-grid"] { padding: 8px 20px 56px; }
  }
</style>
